OL,3,CPolice, Fire and Crime Commissioner
OL,4,Csets out his plan to fight crime
OL,6,FCumbria's Police, Fire and Crime
OL,7,FCommissioner (PFCC) David Allen will
OL,8,Flaunch his first regional plan in
OL,9,FMarch 2025 - setting out his next
OL,10,Fthree years in office.
OL,12,FMr Allen says preventing anti-social
OL,13,Fbehaviour, anti-social driving, rural
OL,14,Fcrime and violence against women and
OL,15,Fgirls are all on his agenda for 2025.
OL,17,FMr Allen will serve Cumbria until the
OL,18,Fnext election in 2028 after taking up
OL,19,Fthe role of PFCC in May 2024.
