OL,3,CPolice, Fire and Crime Commissioner
OL,4,Csets out his plan to fight crime
OL,6,FHe says his aim to tackle violence
OL,7,Fagainst women and girls will become a
OL,8,F"generational piece of work".
OL,10,FHe said: "It's going to take a long
OL,11,Ftime. But in the short term, it's
OL,12,Fabout targeting the perpetrators,
OL,13,Fproviding education in schools as well
OL,14,Fas in various other settings.
OL,16,F"We need to make sure boys in
OL,17,Fparticular understand what it means in
OL,18,Frelation to how you deal and interact
OL,19,Fwith girls and consent."
