OL,3,CPolice, Fire and Crime Commissioner
OL,4,Csets out his plan to fight crime
OL,6,FThe PFCC says Cumbria Police arrested
OL,7,F65 drunk drivers and 84 drug drivers
OL,8,Fthis time last year. Mr Allen believes
OL,9,Fthese "shocking" statistics are
OL,10,Funacceptable.
OL,12,FHe said: "We're going to keep looking
OL,13,Fat targeting individuals who we know
OL,14,Fare drunk or drug driving. The
OL,15,Fintelligence we get from members of
OL,16,Fthe public is used and we do target
OL,17,Fthose individuals.
