OL,3,CPolice, Fire and Crime Commissioner
OL,4,Csets out his plan to fight crime
OL,6,F"There is no place in this society for
OL,7,Fdrinking or drug driving. These
OL,8,Findividuals are putting themselves and
OL,9,Fothers at risk - which could quite
OL,10,Feasily kill people."
OL,12,FDavid Allen also says Cumbria Police
OL,13,Fcurrently have a number of operations
OL,14,Fworking towards key individuals who
OL,15,Fare involved in rural crime.
