OL,3,CPolice, Fire and Crime Commissioner
OL,4,Csets out his plan to fight crime
OL,6,FHe said: "We are targeting organised
OL,7,Fcriminals who we know are involved. We
OL,8,Fhave lots of operations that put
OL,9,Fpatrols out in those rural areas of
OL,10,FCumbria, we are targeting the farms
OL,11,Fwhich we know are going to be hit.
OL,13,F"We are working with farmers to better
OL,14,Fprotect their properties," he added.
